title: Our Very Own Advice Column!
description:
In this episode Jessi and Stew answer questions from their listeners and give advice on situations they get asked about! This is their version of an advice column and will do episodes like this every so often. Remember to follow along on Instagram and submit your advice to be answered on a future episode!
